<plot>Russia, the present. The story of the three Vlasov siblings, Lena, Lyosha, and Olenka continues. Their father, Sergey Ivanovich Vlasov, who, unknown to anyone, had been rescued from the disaster at sea where all had thought he had perished, has returned home alive. Their mother, Nadezhda Nikolaevna, has come out of her coma, and is recovering from her mysterious illness. The family is reunited, and the three siblings are once again in the protective and nurturing arms of their real parents. But, life for the Vlasov family will not return to normal. New troubles await them, which will test their ability to hold on to their love for each other and remain together as a family. Soon, they will learn to struggle as one family against all.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?618672</url></doc>
